extension and retraction means for extending and retracting the inner kelly section partially out of and partially back into the outer kelly section a proportional distance equal to at least about twice a distance that the sled is moved along the mast planar surface, and for preventing slippage of the inner kelly section relative to the outer kelly section, wherein the extension and retraction means has
a downcrowd cable having a first end and a second end,
