rotary drive means attached to the sled and having a drive shaft having an axis, the rotary drive means connection to and rotates a telescopic shaft means, the telescopic shaft means for providing a variable length, the telescopic shaft means having a first end connected to the drive shaft of the rotary drive means, and a second end for attaching an excavation tool,

wherein the first end of the telescopic shaft means is connected to the drive shaft of the rotary drive means,
